data.description:
Recently renovated 2 bedroom 2 bath duplex with ample parking and a spacious private backyard for the kids to run around. Conveniently located. Comes with a new storage shed that doubles as a patio that's perfect for entertaining. There's also a shared dog run for those with fur babies! All appliances included, with a brand new washer and dryer!

Welcome to your new home in the highly sought-after Alamo Heights Area! This freshly remodeled single-unit residence is perfect for those seeking a comfortable and stylish place to rent.

Featuring a spacious 2 bed/2 bath layout, this home provides plenty of room for your living and entertaining needs. With two convenient parking spaces, you and your guests will always find parking a breeze. The generous 1,170 square feet of living space ensures a cozy and inviting atmosphere.

Step into the expansive backyard, ideal for outdoor activities and relaxation. A large covered patio/entertainment area not only offers shelter but also provides extra storage space. Pet lovers will appreciate the upgraded dog yard, complete with artificial turf.

Inside, the newly remodeled kitchen boasts modern stainless steel appliances, elegant quartz countertops, polished concrete floors, and contemporary backsplashes that add a touch of style to your living space. Enjoy brand new fixtures, fully remodeled bedrooms/bathrooms, unique stylistic finishes, custom closets and ample living spaces.

Centrally located, this property offers easy access to a variety of amenities. Whether you're into shopping, dining, or entertainment, everything you need is within reach. With Starbucks and many more shops and restaurants across the street along with easy access to the main highways (410 or 35) it makes commuting a breeze.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this fantastic residence your new home in the desirable Alamo Heights Area. Schedule a showing today!

3 miles from Fort Sam Houston

5 miles from the St. Mary' Strip and The Pearl

9 miles from the Riverwalk

13 miles from Methodist Hospital in Stone Oak

$500 deposit for pets
Renter covers all utilities except Water
